:Class Stark
‚ćĚ Fastify-style HTTP router for Dyalog APL, built on top of Jarvis.
‚ćĚ
‚ćĚ Usage:
‚ćĚ   ‚ćĚ First define your functions, ListUsers, and GetUser, and CreateUser
‚ćĚ   router‚Üź‚éēNEW Stark
‚ćĚ   router.Handlers‚Üź‚éēTHIS
‚ćĚ   '/users'      router.Get   'ListUsers'
‚ćĚ   '/users/{id}' router.Get   'GetUser'
‚ćĚ   '/users'      router.Post ('CreateUser' opts)   ‚ćĚ opts is an APLAN ns with metadata
‚ćĚ   router.Start 8080

    :Field Public  Handlers      ‚ćĚ namespace where handler functions live
