    ‚ąá {r}‚Üź_Register(method path rarg);handler;options;norm;existing
      :Access Private Instance
      :If 1‚Č†‚Č°rarg                           ‚ćĚ nested: ('HandlerName' options)
          (handler options)‚Üźrarg
      :ElseIf ‚ćē‚ćõ‚Č°rarg
          handler‚Üźrarg                     ‚ćĚ simple string
          options‚Üź()
      :Else
        ‚éēSIGNAL ‚äā('EN' 11)('Message' ('STARK: Right argument to Register must be a string (handler name) or a 2-element vector (handler name, options)'))
      :EndIf
      ‚ćĚ Check for duplicate routes: normalize {param} segments so {id} and {user_id} match
      norm‚Üź_NormalizePath path
      :If 0<‚ČĘ_routes
          existing‚Üź((‚éēC¬®_routes.method)‚ąä‚äā‚éēC method)/_routes
          :If 0<‚ČĘexisting
              :If (‚äānorm)‚ąä_NormalizePath¬®existing.pattern
                  ‚éēSIGNAL ‚äā('EN' 11)('Message' ('STARK: Duplicate route: ',method,' ',path,' conflicts with an existing registration'))
              :EndIf
          :EndIf
      :EndIf
      r‚Üź(
        method: method
        pattern: ,path
        handler: handler
        options: options
      )
      _routes,‚Üźr
