    _NormalizePath‚Üź{‚ćĶ/‚ć®~+\‚ąä+/¬Į1 0‚ĆĹ¬®1 ¬Į1√ó‚Üď'{}'‚ąė.=‚ćĶ}

    ‚ąá r‚Üź{value}DebugLevel level
    ‚ćĚ monadic: return 1 if level is within Debug (powers of 2)
    ‚ćĚ dyadic:  return value unless level is within Debug
      r‚Üź‚ą®/((7‚ćī2)‚ä§‚äÉDebug)‚ą®.‚ąß(7‚ćī2)‚ä§level
      :If 0‚Č†‚éēNC'value'
