    ‚ćĚ Route an incoming Jarvis request to the matching handler
    ‚ąá result‚Üź_Dispatch req;routes;r;matched;pp
      :Access Public Instance
      stopIf DebugLevel 64                          ‚ćĚ stop before routing
      routes‚Üź((‚éēC¬®_routes.method)‚ąä‚äā‚éēC req.Method)/_routes
      :For r :In routes
          (matched pp)‚Üźr.pattern pathMatch req.Endpoint
          :If matched
              req.PathParams‚Üźpp
              req.QueryParams‚Üź(‚éēNS '')‚éēVSET{(,‚äÉ‚ćĶ)(2‚äÉ‚ćĶ)}¬®‚Üďreq.QueryParams
              :If '_'=‚äÉr.handler
                  result‚Üź(‚ćér.handler)req          ‚ćĚ internal handler (on Stark)
              :Else
                  :If DebugLevel 32
                      ‚éē‚Üź'STARK: ',req.Method,' ',req.Endpoint,' ‚Üí ',r.handler
                  :EndIf
                  stopIf DebugLevel 2              ‚ćĚ stop before user handler
                  :Trap 0 DebugLevel 1             ‚ćĚ disable trap if bit 1 set (stop on error)
                      result‚Üź(Handlers‚ćér.handler)req
                  :Else
                      ‚éēSIGNAL‚äā‚éēDMX               ‚ćĚ re-signal to let Jarvis return 500
                  :EndTrap
              :EndIf
              :Return
          :EndIf
      :EndFor
      req.Fail 404
      result‚Üź(
        detail: 'Not Found'
      )
